org.biojava.bio.structure.scop

Class ScopDomain

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.biojava.bio.structure.scop.ScopDomain
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    Serializable

    public class ScopDomain
extends Object
implements Serializable
    Container for the information for a domain. Contains a line in the file dir.cla.scop.txt_1.75 e.g d1dlwa_ 1dlw A: a.1.1.1 14982 cl=46456,cf=46457,sf=46458,fa=46459,dm=46460,sp=46461,px=14982
    Author:
    Andreas Prlic
